OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA fine
OL,6,Falbeit fairly breezy evening with
OL,7,Fplenty of late sunshine. Staying dry
OL,8,Fovernight with prolonged clear periods
OL,9,Fand winds gradually easing. Feeling
OL,10,Fsomewhat fresher compared to last
OL,11,Fnight.
OL,12,
OL,13,CSaturday:FMainly sunny in the south
OL,14,Fand becoming warm by the afternoon. A
OL,15,Flittle more cloud further north and
OL,16,Fbreezier and cooler here with an
OL,17,Fisolated light shower possible.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
