OL,5,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FDry on
OL,6,FSunday with periods of hazy sunshine.
OL,7,FStaying mainly dry early next week
OL,8,Fwith some strong sunshine at times but
OL,9,Fshowery rain is possible at times.
OL,10,FWarmer than recently.
